                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Slight chance of a shower in the late afternoon and evening. Winds northerly 25 to 35 km/h. Overnight temperatures falling to around 17 with daytime temperatures reaching the mid 20s.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="3" start-time-local="2026-05-02T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-05-03T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-05-01T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-05-02T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Very high chance of showers, most likely in the morning and afternoon. Winds northerly 25 to 35 km/h turning northwesterly 30 to 45 km/h during the morning then decreasing to 20 to 30 km/h during the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to around 14 with daytime temperatures reaching the low 20s.</text>
