                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Very high chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm in the morning. Winds northwesterly 25 to 35 km/h turning westerly 20 to 30 km/h during the afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to between 8 and 11 with daytime temperatures reaching around 16.</text>
